# 🛠 Keywords & Functions Revised

| Keyword / Function | Use |
|--------------------|-----|
| `if` | Executes a block when the condition is True |
| `elif` | Checks another condition if the previous one is False |
| `else` | Executes when all previous conditions are False |
| `match` | Performs pattern matching based on a value |
| `case` | Defines different cases inside a match statement |
| `for` | Iterates over a sequence |
| `while` | Executes repeatedly while a condition is True |
| `break` | Terminates the loop immediately |
| `continue` | Skips the current iteration |
| `range()` | Generates a sequence of numbers |

